    "headline": "IFF to Release Second Quarter 2026 Results on August 4, 2026",
    "summary": "NEW YORK, July 09, 2026--IFF (NYSE: IFF) today announced that it will release its second quarter 2026 earnings results following the market close on Tuesday, August 4, 2026. The management team will host a live webcast on Wednesday, August 5, 2026, at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss results and outlook with the investor community.",
